## [v1.0.0-rc.2] - 2025-04-24

### ✨ Features
- Configure CHANGELOG and RELEASE_NOTES management for streamlined documentation processes.
- Validate and test configurations on an empty repository to ensure initial setup integrity.
- Configure using old module version to maintain compatibility with legacy systems.
- Integrate gptmodule for enhanced functionality and performance.

### 🗑️ Removed
- Remove helm chart templates from the app project to simplify project structure.

### 🔧 Maintenance
- Update CHANGELOG entries to reflect the latest changes and improvements.
