## [v1.0.0-rc.2] - 2025-04-24

### ✨ Features
- Configure CHANGELOG generation to automate release documentation
- Implement RELEASE_NOTES configuration for streamlined release processes
- Validate and test with an empty repository scenario to ensure robustness
- Configure using an old module version for compatibility testing
- Set up and configure gptmodule to enhance plugin functionality

### 🗑️ Removed
- Remove helm chart templates from app project to streamline project structure

### 🔧 Maintenance
- Update CHANGELOG entries for consistency and clarity
