## [v1.0.0-rc.2] - 2025-04-24

### ✨ Features
- Configure and validate `RELEASE_NOTES` for improved release process management.
- Add configuration for using old module version to ensure compatibility with legacy systems.
- Implement configuration and testing for scenarios with an empty repository to enhance robustness.
- Introduce `gptmodule` configuration for advanced module management.

### 🔧 Maintenance
- Remove helm chart templates from app project to streamline project structure.
- Update CHANGELOG to reflect recent changes and improvements.
